		<span><strong>Attitude</strong></span> <span>3lb weight limit</span><span>8" hardened steel disc</span><span id="end">2 time champion, 5 time medalist</span>
		<p id="desc">Attitude is all about kinetic energy. This three pounder spins an abnormally large disc at 3200 rpm, intending to transfer as much of that energy as possible into its opponents. The unintended consequence of such a large weapon is the gyroscopic forces created when the weapon is spinning— Attitude becomes quite difficult to maneuver. 
		</p>
