		<p id="desc">Keep it simple, stupid. Tiny Terror doesn’t have a flashy weapon because it doesn’t need one. For this robot, it is all about driving skill— out maneuver the opponent and dominate purely through aggression and tactical driving. Although not technically challenging to design or construct, Tiny Terror is one of my most successful robots.
